{"tid":478024,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透討論] 有無人睇左澳至尊動作新戲《狂獸 The Brink》","createTime":"2017-11-23T15:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T07:37:11.000Z","uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fa32d9730ca89c4dcded7327c011dd6adcb93de3","tid":478024,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/14853118_1689039968009303_2204117589532962797_o.jpg?oh=e6f60d521562e697ec5fbd0aff651084&amp;oe=5AA76577\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F14853118_1689039968009303_2204117589532962797_o.jpg%3Foh%3De6f60d521562e697ec5fbd0aff651084%26oe%3D5AA76577&h=ef6eb1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22552374_1849510131962285_7146912170894400975_n.jpg?oh=d8880f55f3f6511b6b7550b75aae5699&amp;oe=5A8C8583\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22552374_1849510131962285_7146912170894400975_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dd8880f55f3f6511b6b7550b75aae5699%26oe%3D5A8C8583&h=e45a58d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gb-o5Dk_AXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgb-o5Dk_AXM&d=ndIlKwG8bi9xNXoEHtRbqZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=db9b8026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gb-o5Dk_AXM</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 張晉、余文樂由水面打到水底！<br />\n⚠️ 當正義變成歇斯底里，當貪慾變到迷失人性！<br />\n⚠️ 新晉導演李子俊，聯乘金像得主李忠志打破本地動作片極限！<br />\n<br />\n【動作特技鉅製《狂獸》鐵定11月23日上映！】<br />\n🌕釜山電影節觀眾勁讚動作稱霸！水面打到水底成焦點，充滿港片特色！<br />\n🌕釜山電影節世界首映好評滿載<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a080f9016fb9bca653ce3544e6837af4f45f13","tid":478024,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"余文樂打得掂唔掂？"},{"pid":"04e88942587249d7e098569be95c911662236667","tid":478024,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"又一部新導演既戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套戲都幾難拍，特別係中段水底戲同尾段船上大戰<br />\n文戲麻麻地，不過唔係重點，比例上好少<br />\n主要賣點動作戲睇得幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正過暑假套貪狼好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd60a36e518ebe800ea2f861feea07c9ba9be3dc","tid":478024,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>余文樂打得掂唔掂？</blockquote><br />\n算係咁 有鏡頭就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過成套戲佢壓住把聲講野聽落去好唔自然"},{"pid":"e8a2e2144256a22f37d42d0b26266d0493aaee57","tid":478024,"uid":159183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"不過睇張晉打都已經值得入場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad4556e64b2da02b536ccfba99737bd5a4025c1","tid":478024,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"樂仔沙包黎呀昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a48a95803b509f69d2a35bdadac7b7db30dc4e","tid":478024,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你<br />\n夜晚打風潛落水底唔知邊度黎嘅光視野咁清晰"},{"pid":"e9a1b4682672b40e0e6fff498ebc398611aadb65","tid":478024,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩屌你<br />\n夜晚打風潛落水底唔知邊度黎嘅光視野咁清晰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6817b0981c30a8b3c50cb0b8b8018dba4cbb18ee","tid":478024,"uid